com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface GeneratorLpVar

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GeneratorElement, GeneratorTupleMember, GeneratorVar, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratorLpVarImpl

    public interface GeneratorLpVar
extends GeneratorVar
    A representation of the model object 'Generator Lp Var'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Lower Bound
    • Upper Bound
    • Objective Coeff
    • Lp Term
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getGeneratorLpVar()
